            <h1>Welcome to the Global Nutrition Community</h1>
            <p>The Global Nutrition Community is a vibrant network of nutrition professionals, students, and enthusiasts<br>
               dedicated to promoting optimal health and well-being through evidence-based nutrition practices.<br>
               Founded in November 2023 by Rhoda Olorunseyi.<br>
               A seasoned health coach, health educator, registered nutritionist, project manager, and public speaker,<br>
               our community is passionate about empowering individuals to take control of their health and<br>
               fostering a supportive environment for nutrition professionals to thrive.<br>
            </p>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>To build a global network of responsible and respected nutrition leaders,<br>
               providing access to resources, tools, and support for our members to excel<br>
               in their careers and make a positive impact in their communities.
            </p>
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>A world where nutrition professionals are valued and recognized for their expertise,<br>
               and individuals prioritize informed dietary choices for optimal health and well-being.
